				<td colspan="2"><span>Thanks Dermei.
<br />

<br />
Please note that at the time I wrote this, it was from the perspective of a SUB 51 Bard, I don't have any &quot;fancy gear&quot; and I don't have the lvl 51 Travel song.
<br />

<br />
As for User Interfaces, not everyone wants to use those specialized ones, hotkeys do work well enough, but for those who want, that is a good idea.
<br />

<br />
As to pounding keys, I hate trying to do that over and over, I have enough ailments as is, I don't need to increase my chances of Corpral Tunnel.
<br />

<br />
And I should have noted the &quot;end swarm&quot; tactics which I forgot.  I ususally get down to the last 2 and just toggle back and forth dotting them down to death.  Takes a little while, but do able.
<br />

<br />
Again, thank you for your input.  It's helpful.</span></td>
